text: Hul Kimhuy (born 7 April 2000) is a Cambodian footballer who plays for Boeung Ket in the Cambodian League and the Cambodia U-23. ==Club career== Hul Kimhuy made his senior debut in Cambodia League on 16 March 2019 Vs Phnom Penh Crown. ==International career== Hul Kimhuy made his senior debut in 2020 AFC U-23 Championship qualification against Australia national under-23 soccer team on 22 March 2019. == External links == *Hul Kimhuy at NationalFootballTeams Category:Living people Category:2000 births Category:People from Takéo Province Category:Cambodian footballers Category:Cambodia international footballers Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:Competitors at the 2019 Southeast Asian Games
